    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[0]
      value: Good luck **[color=#CFB32D]TERRY[/color]**!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[1]
      value: 'You got this **[color=#CFB32D]TERRY[/color]**! '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[2]
      value: Were the notes I left behind helpful? I like to leave them around the
        office to ease the onboarding experience, especially since I know how **[color=#FF6600]Perry[/color]**
        is.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[3]
      value: Actually don't answer that, you look a bit tired. Hope you get some
        rest tonight and I'll catch you at my desk first thing tomorrow!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueLines.Array.data[4]
      value: Tomorrow, we go to my desk!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: tertiaryDialogue.Array.size
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: secondaryDialogue.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: objectiveToGive.Array.data[0]
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: Before you go talk to **[color=#FF6600]PERRY[/color]**, you're gonna
        want to grab the **FIRE EXTINGUISHER**... trust me.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[1].defaultText
      value: '**IMPORTANT: YOUR [color=#CFB32D]TERRY[/color] FORM IS A REQUIREMENT
        TO PICK UP AND USE THE FIRE EXTINGUISHER.**'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
