        WATER** over at **[color=#153CBF]JERRY[/color]** and **[color=#1FCD00]CARRIE'S[/color]**
        desks. I'm gonna need you to do that over here too.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[2].defaultText
      value: Also for some reason, everything is on fire. Can you go ahead and **PUT
        OUT THE FIRES**  while you're at it?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: baseDialogue.Array.data[3].defaultText
      value: You have 10 minutes kiddo, get to it!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: secondaryDialogue.Array.data[0].defaultText
      value: I know I'm your **[color=#FF6600]BOSS[/color]**, but we're also family
        now. Think of me like you're cool **[color=#FF6600]UNCLE PERRY[/color]**.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: secondaryDialogue.Array.data[1].defaultText
      value: It's really not that hard. Just **TURN ON THE POWER**, **TURN OFF THE
        WATER**, and **PUT OUT THE FIRES**.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3493604527745461607, guid: 89b2ae7bccf9f426999e81c797e9ff4e,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: events.Array.data[0].m_PersistentCalls.m_Calls.Array.size
